@startuml
skinparam style strictuml
skinparam dpi 180
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 17
skinparam defaultFontColor #1F2937
skinparam ArrowColor #315780
skinparam ArrowThickness 1.6
skinparam activityBorderColor #315780
skinparam activityBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam activityDiamondBorderColor #315780
skinparam activityDiamondBackgroundColor #E9F0F7
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #F3F7FA
skinparam noteBorderColor #8496A8
skinparam titleFontColor #17324D
skinparam titleFontSize 24

title Multi-agent decision process

start
:<b>1. Market intelligence</b>\nOpportunity Scout selects relevant markets\nResearch Agent qualifies external information;
:<b>2. Portfolio strategy</b>\nStrategist builds the multi-asset playbook\nfrom market data and current positions;
:<b>3. Trade proposal</b>\nTrader selects the action, allocation,\nleverage and exit policy;
:<b>4. Neutral assessment</b>\nSimulator calculates margin, loss, funding\nand execution consequences;
:<b>5. Final review</b>\nRisk Review confirms, adjusts or cancels\nthe initial proposal;

if (Executable action?) then (Yes)
  :<b>6. Controlled execution</b>\nValidate operations, persist the intent,\nsign the order and reconcile fills;
else (No)
  :Record HOLD / CANCEL decision;
endif

:<b>7. Observability</b>\nPublish decisions, costs, positions and P&L\nto the operator dashboard;
stop

note right
  Separation of responsibilities
  • agents analyse and propose
  • deterministic services validate
  • only the executor can sign an order
end note
@enduml
